Class DuckControlService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zodoto.util.ducks.DuckControlService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DuckControl

    public class DuckControlService
extends java.lang.Object
implements DuckControl
    This class is the core of the duck. It controls the supply of keys, provides keys when requested and more keys from the source as needed.
